                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6329" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0984</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9426 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“金钰”其外，败絮其中：疯狂石头的谢幕</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Gold and jade without, rubbish within.——In terms of the case of financial fraud in HUBEI EASTERN GOLD JADE CO., LTD.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄怡，侯媛敏，蔡世霖，林丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东方金钰股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东方金钰；财务舞弊；GONE理论；审计失败</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Eastern Gold Jade;financial fraud;Theories of financial fraud GONE;Audit failure</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，上市公司财务舞弊行为层出不穷，严重破环了证券市场的健康发展，损害了利益相关者的切身利益，引发投资者对资本市场的信任危机。东方金钰作为我国翡翠行业“第一股”，2020年4月24日被证监部门爆出财务舞弊行为，随即在资本市场引起哗然。调查发现，东方金钰在2016-2018年期间通过虚构销售和采购合同虚增营业收入和营业成本，虚增了利润3.6亿元，给公司和股民造成不可估计的损失。本案例以东方金钰财务舞弊为主线，描述东方金钰的发展历程、财务舞弊的动机和手段以及舞弊所产生的后果进行概述，培养学生对上市公司财务舞弊的识别能力，了解财务舞弊的形成机理，学会透过官方公告与财务报表信息的表象看到上市公司经济行为的本质，为防范上市公司财务舞弊提出建议。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, the financial fraud of listed companies has emerged in an endless stream, which has seriously broken the healthy development of the securities market, damaged the vital interests of stakeholders, and triggered the crisis of trust of investors in the capital market. HUBEI EASTERN GOLD JADE CO., LTD., as the &quot;first share&quot; in China&#39;s jade industry, was exposed to financial fraud by the securities regulatory department on April 24, 2020, which immediately caused uproar in the capital market. The survey found that from 2016 to 2018 this company falsely increased its operating revenue and operating costs through fictitious sales and procurement contracts, and inflated its profit of 360 million yuan, which has caused the company and the stockholders the inestimable loss. This case takes the financial fraud of Eastern Gold Jade as the main line, describes the development process of this company, the motives and means of its financial fraud and the consequences resulting from it, aiming to train students to identify and understand the formation mechanism of financial fraud, to see the essence of the economic behavior through the official announcements and financial statements, and to put forward suggestions for preventing the financial fraud of listed companies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《审计学》、《审计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">GONE理论的定义及内容；财务舞弊的概念及常见手段；审计失败的概念、财务舞弊的相关法律；财务舞弊的识别框架及方法；反舞弊机制和内部控制制度</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
